http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/16-hurt-in-bus-accident-near-Sindhanur/article14492812.ece

 As many as 16 people were injured when a bus by which they were travelling overturned near Sindhanur on Saturday. The injured were rushed to Sindhanur government hospital. Officials’ visitThe bus, operated by North-Eastern Karnataka Road Transport Corporation, was bound from Singapur to Sindhanur when driver lost control. Senior officials NEKRTC and police visited the spot. 